一個十零歲學生<br />\n對讀書進唔進步根本好疏離<br />\n但如果佢投入左項運動，例如籃球<br />\n點樣令自己進步<br />\n點樣同人哋合作<br />\n點樣可以取勝<br />\n呢啲問題其實係遠比「讀好書」困難<br />\n而且學生會有更大嘅熱情去思考呢啲問題<br />\n所以重點係要令學生培養到自己嘅興趣<br />\n投入熱情"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T01:01:23.000Z","msg":"所以中國同之後香港都唔會搞呢啲<br />\n有得你班仆街死讀爛讀<br />\n<br />\n就係唔想啲細路識得同人合作同思考未來<br />\n咁先可以方便洗腦同控制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb43a28d438431713484aed3037e0bdc898a0db","tid":2500680,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T01:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d948224eda8968ef8ea3a517dd95497c4a5f5cb0","tid":2500680,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T01:51:56.000Z","msg":"JK課外活動揾爸爸"},{"pid":"1309bb04c360bc3ad25b749a511a57619b7d0857","tid":2500680,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T01:52:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>又係你條撚屌五毛, 舊聞洗時事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"39935bbd5137e45a61f501cd367df70923eddb3d","tid":2500680,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T01:52:56.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"1a13b7f9f32eb850bda77f84a09fe22682fa516e","tid":2500680,"uid":329977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"64aab57b3a68726210c0ce022267c1aaa589e313","tid":2500680,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T00:46:33.000Z","msg":"日本高中生生活係咪日日欺凌與被欺凌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚恐怖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T01:56:05.000Z","msg":"所以最唔想去exchange嘅地方就去韓國同日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好驚埋唔到堆"},{"pid":"2b03270cbf06f828934435b9c8daa89be6a0dbfa","tid":2500680,"uid":287107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s